-Yes.

704
00:37:04.330 --> 00:37:06.257
Okay. All right. "To not..."
Give me some.

705
00:37:06.291 --> 00:37:09.844
"I've even made
a large donation to NAMI.

706
00:37:09.878 --> 00:37:11.679
the National Alliance
on Mental Illness..."

707
00:37:11.713 --> 00:37:12.847
-Dru.
-Yeah?

708
00:37:12.881 --> 00:37:14.024
